title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - Gene Machine
description:
What is Guy Raz doing with that big ladder? And what does that have to do with genes? We’ve got questions AND answers on this relatively relatable round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! We’re challenging you to find the facts from the fiction about genetics!
